1) Answer the question
2) Assign it to someone else
3) Reject it (but only if it's a duplicate submission or inappropriate)

Please resolve this question before 
<%= @respond_by.strftime("%A, %B %e, %Y, %l:%M %p") %> UTC (EST + 5:00). 

